# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# istio.env — Istio deployment configuration
# Generated by OpenTofu at apply time. Do not edit manually.
#
# Sourced automatically by 2-asm scripts.
# Override individual values on the command line or by setting env vars
# before running the scripts.
